{"tid":1026783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實佢個心仲有冇我?","createTime":"2019-02-18T10:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T11:06:02.000Z","uid":146246,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"514f17910f7a1a94c493e4098cd7290b4c78e5c3","tid":1026783,"uid":146246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=女同學a <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=女同學b<br />\n話說小弟中一果陣 主動認識咗同班嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n          過程進展得好順利 我地嘅關係一直好曖昧 一直持續咗半年有多 但並冇任何一方主動表白<br />\n <br />\n只喺每一晚都保持住要傾幾個鐘電話<br />\n<br />\n我地有承諾過 當wts聊天記錄達到520頁之後(當時f1冇諗過520頁究竟有幾多)就互相同對方講自<br />\n<br />\n己中意嘅人喺邊個<br />\n<br />\n          但結果冇耐之後喺校外嘅補習社到小弟本人認識咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 相識冇耐我就對佢產生咗極大嘅興<br />\n<br />\n趣 我開始將目標轉移至呢位女仔嘅身上 而漸漸放棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n         <br />\n         之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咗我女朋友 而<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似意識到呢件事(我唔肯定) 佢都開始冇再揾我 <br />\n<br />\n         我知自己仆街仔 我知自己賤男 但當時仲身為f1仔嘅我 真喺冇諗咁多嘢...<br />\n<br />\n         同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相處咗兩個幾月 我開始發現佢根本唔適合我 每次傾計都feel到好明顯嘅代溝  某日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為中意咗第二個而主動向我提出咗分手 當刻我真喺好後悔 後悔自己之前作出嘅每一個決定  <br />\n<br />\n因為我覺得對唔住 而且冇資格再揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我之後都冇對佢有任何表示<br />\n<br />\n       時間過得好快 呢五年黎 我同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都冇乜再有接觸 加上黎緊四月就要考dse 我地大家都已經進<br />\n<br />\n入備戰狀態 更加冇時間揾對方 但結果就喺幾日前 喺我fd本紀念冊見到佢寫嘅一段嘢:我f1的<br />\n<br />\n確中意過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢之後都冇乜理過我 所以我就算了..如果唔喺 佢已經喺我喺呢間學校第一個亦喺<br />\n<br />\n唯一一個男朋友 不過依家已經冇可能了..<br />\n<br />\n      我好努力放棄過佢 但真喺冇成功過..六年黎 因為我個心都仲有佢 所以做咗6年嘅毒撚 冇拍過<br />\n<br />\n任何拖 呢段嘢可唔可以證明其實我仲有機會？我依家仲應唔應該主動穩翻佢？"},{"pid":"5d45ce055d28c7e7ff6a37c7232012301532812f","tid":1026783,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"629f5970ab4c35592d03b76e6fda21854832abae","tid":1026783,"uid":113102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d45ce055d28c7e7ff6a37c7232012301532812f","tid":1026783,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:03:01.000Z","msg":"有冇冇埋右？"},{"pid":"282a37e3b5c2d9a0d1ff732286000ba2ad850549","tid":1026783,"uid":146246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d45ce055d28c7e7ff6a37c7232012301532812f","tid":1026783,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住佢.."},{"pid":"334f727180f7ea3534f81f34fa0a13d3a7d695ad","tid":1026783,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d45ce055d28c7e7ff6a37c7232012301532812f","tid":1026783,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"你唔捉佢個穩字？"},{"pid":"a5dc24e2e7830d12a766aae9e0b1545e027625de","tid":1026783,"uid":166188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d45ce055d28c7e7ff6a37c7232012301532812f","tid":1026783,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"搵唔到錯字？"},{"pid":"e05ef152dccfd467312de67111152d52c1fc707c","tid":1026783,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T11:04:34